On this page

Disk Format ​

Open CMD then type

sh
diskpart

A window should open

List all the disk ​

sh
list disk

Select the disk you want to clean ​

sh
selec disk

Clean the disk ​

sh
clean

Create partition ​

sh
create partition primary

Format the disk (choose the format for your use) ​

sh
format fs=fat32 quick

Finally active the partition ​

sh
active

Your disk is ready to use
